               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17360225-2-person33">
                  Ashton 
                  Broad 
               <interp inst="t17360225-2-person33" type="surname" value="Broad"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17360225-2-person33" type="given" value="Ashton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17360225-2-person33" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw a Man, January the 24th come down the Stairs of a Ware-house in an Alley on <placeName id="t17360225-2-crimeloc9">Cox's Key</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17360225-2-crimeloc9" type="placeName" value="Cox's Key"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17360225-2-crimeloc9" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17360225-2-off6 t17360225-2-crimeloc9"></join>, and the Prisoner followed him, with something ty'd up in his Apron: I took him by the Collar, and he endeavouring to get from me, dragg'd me to the top of the Alley. I called for Assistance, and we took 20 lb. of Sugar upon him. Upon searching the Ware-house, we found a Door open in the Garret, and the Head of a Hogshead of Sugar taken out; we weigh'd the Goods, and found half a Hundred, and 22lb. missing; we compared what we took upon the Prisoner, with that in the Hogshead, and it answered directly.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17360225-2-person34">
                  John 
                  Davis 
               <interp inst="t17360225-2-person34" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
