                     <interp inst="t17360225-2-person34" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Upon Mr. Broad's calling out, I went to assist him; and took the Prisoner with this Sugar upon him; we secured him, and found the Hogshead broke, from whence the Sugar was taken.</p>
               <p>The Prisoner in his Defence, said, the Man that got off, employ'd him to carry the Sugar out of the Alley, and was to give him a Pot of Beer; but could not give any account of him. <rs id="t17360225-2-verdict10" type="verdictDescription">
